{"tid":2124604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：去年全港有993人輕生","createTime":"2020-07-25T13:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T13:38:53.000Z","uid":36044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2b2ce11b18e9c5d58d060464bccd29cb0a05cf6a","tid":2124604,"uid":36044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會引述死因庭報告指，去年全港有993人輕生，較2018年增加38宗，男性佔6成半。以年齡群組計算，60歲或以上人士的輕生比率最高，與以往一樣。<br />\n<br />\n總幹事曾展國表示，去年自殺數字輕微上升，死因庭沒有解釋背後的原因，因此難以作出評估，但他指，長者在最後生命階段面對特別大的危機，男性亦偏向裝強，可能未有及時找幫助，容易「爆煲」輕生。<br />\n<br />\n曾展國提到，去年3月至12月，熱線中心收到929宗求助是與社會事件有關，由10歲至70歲都有，少部分有低至高危的自殺危機，大部分只是情緒受社會事件影響，網上聊天求助亦有97宗。<br />\n<br />\n被問到本港失業率上升的影響，曾展國表示，不敢說經濟對自殺有多大影響，但過往沙士時，經濟嚴重下滑，對自殺數字有影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，該會去年共接獲近1萬3千宗求助，較前年減少4%，當中50至59歲求助者相對最多，佔總數近2成，9歲以下求助者有12人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539808-20200725.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539808-20200725.htm&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=6ef148f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539808-20200725.htm&h=f414a626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539808-20200725.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8bae8ede26fb63b6c695b0c5a4642d40761d81db","tid":2124604,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fb48a71d2e0900f32c459ad85845f0a93664b9","tid":2124604,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"又維穩"},{"pid":"0bea047b4919827ea0e3a6fb63cafe1ddbb41995","tid":2124604,"uid":36044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:31:11.000Z","msg":"香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會公布2019年自殺統計數字，去年經死因裁判法庭報告的自殺個案共有993宗，較前年上升38宗，升幅約4%，即每10萬人中有13.25人因自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n不過，993宗個案中有33宗是「不能確定是意外或蓄意傷害」，13宗為「溺斃」，12宗是「服毒」。而能夠確定死因個案中，超過一半是從高處墮下，其次是吊死，佔約20%，燒炭則排第三位，有13%。"},{"pid":"6e97157f0a5aa4636df2701ea7c2d047f61d2fe2","tid":2124604,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:31:32.000Z","msg":"被殺當自殺<br />\n<br />\n法醫都係呢個暴政幫兇<br />\n<br />\n應予以制裁"},{"pid":"fea4b50e1922735da92584bb8e2aaedf473b4dbc","tid":2124604,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:31:51.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9860d5a90fb34c1442437ce02c74021579dc4ac9","tid":2124604,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8bae8ede26fb63b6c695b0c5a4642d40761d81db","tid":2124604,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea204fcb18b7e5bb682867235928ff4cfc50742","tid":2124604,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bae8ede26fb63b6c695b0c5a4642d40761d81db","tid":2124604,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}